好多。雖然老邱係令到亞視有賺，但係出名孤鳩寒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n80年代中到90年代頭都係蕭亮做亞視報幕<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=T5Zope6sY0Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DT5Zope6sY0Y&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPNagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=5b302ba9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=T5Zope6sY0Y</a>"}]}